celebrations that the potential existed for serious rifts 
we are friends not allies said mei renyi an associate 
professor of american studies at the beijing university of foriegn 
studies he could not be interviewed now because he is being 
investigated for supporting the democracy movement 
our systems are different our ideologies are different he 
said then our expectations should be realistic 
