former hud secretary samuel r pierce jrs 
lawyer accused the justice department monday of giving an 
offthewall reason for not paying pierces legal expenses from 
a congressional investigation 
a justice department spokesman said it was just an 
interpretation of law 
pierce twice refused to answer questions when he appeared before 
