the government news media said 
monday that 149 of the 355 demonstrators arrested during an 
antigovernment protest will be charged with violating public order 
the communist party daily rude pravo said the 149 were detained 
for 48 hours and all of the others arrested during the 
demonstration saturday in prague were released soon after they had 
been seized 
